Package hu.bme.mit.theta.cfa.dsl.gen

Interface CfaDslListener

All Superinterfaces:
org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
All Known Implementing Classes:
CfaDslBaseListener
public interface CfaDslListener extends org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
This interface defines a complete listener for a parse tree produced by CfaDslParser.
